			<div class="content" id="post-content-3816244">
									

<p><em><sub>The jig is up, the news is out</sub></em><br />
<em><sub>They finally found me!</sub></em><br />
<em><sub>The renegade who had it made</sub></em><br />
<em><sub>Retrieved for a bounty!</sub></em><br />
<em><sub>Never more to go astray</sub></em><br />
<em><sub>This'll be the end today</sub></em><br />
<em><sub><a href="https://youtu.be/ZXhuso4OTG4">Of the wanted man!</a></sub></em></p>
<hr />
<p>I can't stop writing Broken Masquerade. It's taking over my life. I also want to give a shoutout to <a href="http://sexycontainmentprocedures.tumblr.com/post/173395150172/youre-hands-down-one-of-if-not-the-best-writer-on">this anon on Tumblr a few weeks ago</a> who gave me the summary of my Foundation that I'd never been able to articulate. I wouldn't not have been able to write this properly without the chain of thought those messages inspired, so thanks, anon.</p>
<p>This is also a Doomsday Contest entry for <a href="/amnesticization">Team Fuhgeddaboutit</a>.</p>
<p>Thank you to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/absentmindednihilist" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2812984); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2812984&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1527559440" alt="AbsentmindedNihilist" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2812984)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/absentmindednihilist" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2812984); return false;">AbsentmindedNihilist</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sly161" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2969980); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2969980&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1527559440" alt="Sly161" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2969980)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sly161" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2969980); return false;">Sly161</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2320004); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2320004&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1527559440" alt="Rimple" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2320004)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2320004); return false;">Rimple</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wrongjohnsilver" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2000367); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2000367&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1527559440" alt="WrongJohnSilver" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2000367)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wrongjohnsilver" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2000367); return false;">WrongJohnSilver</a></span> for feedback. Carolina Beach coast image edited by me and source is Wikimedia Commons <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Carolina_Beach_Pier.jpg">here</a>. All other images created by me.</p>

